http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5158807/Jeppview_3_Airac_0901_complete
(you have to rename the Label of the cd or the file if a error message pops out and says: unrecognized disk)
After you installed them run and activate the programms again on your computer.
Now you should be able install the new datacycles without any code and don't  forget to change the time settings.
